AgentsData/QClaw/WorkSpace/
AgentsData/WorkBuddy/WorkSpace/
AgentsData/SharedProjects/
AgentsData/ClaudeCodeCLI/projects/
AgentsData/ClaudeCodeCLI/hooks/
AgentsData/ClaudeCodeCLI/Backups/soul-auto/
