.env
.env.*
**/API_Key*
**/api_key*
**/*密码*
**/*password*
**/*secret*
**/Git公钥*
**/SSH*key*
Docs/日常应用/API_Key.txt
Docs/日常应用/Git公钥.txt
Docs/日常应用/*密码*.txt

